## Mobile (React Native + Expo)

- Functional components only — no class components
- StyleSheet.create() for all styles — never inline style objects (performance)
- expo-secure-store for sensitive data (auth tokens) — never AsyncStorage for secrets
- Platform differences: Platform.OS checks or .ios.tsx / .android.tsx file extensions
- No web-only APIs (window, document, localStorage) — use RN equivalents
- React Query for all server state — same patterns as web
- Zustand for global local state (auth session, user preferences)
- EAS Build for production — never deprecated `expo build` command
- Deep linking: configure app.json scheme for both iOS and Android
- Push notifications: expo-notifications with proper permission requests
